MediCare Hospital Website
Project Overview
This project is a responsive website for MediCare Hospital, providing information about services, doctors, patient testimonials, and contact details for inquiries.

Features
Home Page: Displays an overview of the hospital and its key services.
Services Page: Lists medical services offered by the hospital.
Doctors Page: Showcases hospital doctors with their specializations.
Testimonials Page: Displays patient reviews and success stories.
Contact Us Page: Enables users to reach out via a form, phone number, or email.
Appointment Booking: Allows users to schedule medical appointments.
Responsive Design: Works on different devices (desktop, tablet, and mobile).
Image Slideshow: Interactive image slider on the homepage.
Form Validation: Ensures proper submission of contact details and appointment forms.

Technologies Used
HTML5: For structuring the pages.
CSS3: For styling and layout.
JavaScript: For interactivity and form handling.

How to Run the Project
Download the project folder.
Open the index.html file in a web browser.

Deployment
The website is deployed on:
 https://enock122.github.io/final-project/#services

